{
  "stem": "14060.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One of the two important events which left clear memories in my mind was, first of all, in March, 1938, when Hitler marched into Austria.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "History I don't wish to repeat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's well recorded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were sitting-- it happened to be on a Friday.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were sitting at the Friday-night dinner, being religious Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And having been so Orthodox Jews, we did not use cars-- we had access to cars-- or, for that reason, even electricity.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We used to have a little clock which-- today, you use a proper time clock.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But those days, you used one of these alarm clocks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had a little wire arrangement which then automatically switched it off at a certain hour.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then we had another one, which was attached to another light switch, which then turned it on at a given time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now-- so whilst certain technical advances were not there, one could work one's way around.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Anyway, on a Friday night, I heard Hitler's speech already, all what was happening.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "On that Friday, it was great excitement, the terrible events happening in Austria.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My father's younger brother was in Austria, in Baden bei Wien, and some other relatives.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And many, many people in our town had close relatives in-- across the border in Burgenland, which was practically a kilometer from the town center was the border.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I remember, suddenly a doorbell goes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I, being the younger one-- I was eight years old-- I ran quickly to the lounge-room window, because we were sitting in the dining room, which was more to the garden, to see who the person is in front of the house.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I see a taxi, not stopping, but the engine still going.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
